verbose_text: Small differences were found for MMP2 in lung tissue as measured by 2 -ddCT which was higher in the group ventilated for 30s (1.1 (0.9-1.4)) compared to the 60s (0.8 (0.6-0.96)) and 90s group (0.6 (0.59-0.96)), p = 0.043 and p = 0.02 respectively, whereas expression of ICAM-1 was higher in the 30 s group (1.01 (0.86-1.09)) compared to 60 s (0.82 (0.79-0.94)), p = 0.012.
